CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 13, 1954, pg. 21, reads: "Jackie Robinson - Bats for Brotherhood - ...Below, Jackie is shown with Bernard McCormick and C. F. Kortner, after he had addressed some 1,400 students at Schenley High. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Bernard McCormick, Brooklyn Dodgers baseball player Jackie Robinson, and C. F. Kortner, standing in front of landscape painting in Schenley High School
